headline: CAH Expands Distribution Network With Indianapolis Facility
summary: Cardinal Health accelerates its multi-year supply chain transformation with a new flagship Indianapolis distribution center, reinforcing automation-driven efficiency while building on recent logistics expansions in Ohio and Texas.
